@page "/about-us"
@layout CheckoutLayout
@rendermode @(new InteractiveServerRenderMode(prerender: false))

<PageTitle>About Us | EnergyWay</PageTitle>

<div class="page-background-shared">
    <div class="overlay-shared">
        <div class="container py-5">

            <div class="glass-card-about">
                <!-- 1. Header Section with the new Logo -->
                <div class="about-header text-center">
                    @* --- START: LOGO MODIFICATION --- *@
                    <img src="/images/logo4.jpg" alt="PLS Company Logo" class="company-logo-banner" />
                    @* --- END: LOGO MODIFICATION --- *@
                    <h1 class="mt-4">About The Project</h1>
                    <p class="lead-text">This project was developed during our training at **PLS (Petrochemicals Logistic Services)**.</p>
                </div>

                <hr class="section-divider" />

                <!-- 2. Project Idea Section (No changes here) -->
                <div class="about-section">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 3.096 10.047 9.005 9.005 0 0 1 5.9 8.19.75.75 0 0 1-1.49.174 7.5 7.5 0 0 0-14.993 0 .75.75 0 0 1-1.49-.174 9.005 9.005 0 0 1 5.9-8.19A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 12 2.5ZM8 8a4 4 0 1 0 8 0 4 4 0 0 0-8 0Z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-content">
                        <h2>Project Idea</h2>
                        <p>The project is a **fully integrated system** developed for the company, covering all main roles. Each role has its **own secure interface**, and no one can access another role’s page or permissions.</p>
                        <ul class="roles-list">
                            <li><strong>Company Owner (Manager ):</strong> Has a dedicated dashboard to manage everything in the company.</li>
                            <li><strong>Warehouse Manager:</strong> Responsible for managing the stock and monitoring product availability.</li>
                            <li><strong>Delivery Representative:</strong> Has a special page to handle delivery tasks and orders.</li>
                            <li><strong>Customer (End User):</strong> Can browse the website and purchase products easily.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="mt-3">The entire system is connected to a **MySQL database** to ensure accuracy and efficiency, using **ASP.NET Core Web API** and **Blazor**.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="section-divider" />

                <!-- 3. Team Members Section -->
                <div class="about-section">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.5 19.5a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h9a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0v-.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5h-9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5v.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0v-.5Z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-content">
                        <h2>Team Members</h2>
                        <p class="team-members">
                            Mina Medhat William & Antonios Sameh Samer
                        </p>
                        <p class="special-thanks mt-3">
                            💡 Special thanks to <strong>Eng. Aya Abdelhafez</strong> for her great support and guidance throughout the project.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="section-divider" />

                <!-- 4. The Company Section with the new Photo -->
                <div class="about-section">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4.5 2.25a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5v16.5a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h15a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5V3.75a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5h-15ZM9 6a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-4.5A.75.75 0 0 1 9 6Zm-1.5 3.75a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h7.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-7.5a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75ZM9 15a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-4.5A.75.75 0 0 1 9 15Z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-content">
                        <h2>The Company</h2>
                        <p>
                            This project was developed during our training at <strong>PLS (Petrochemicals Logistic Services )</strong>.
                            We are truly grateful to the company for providing us with this opportunity and support, which helped us turn our idea into a real working project.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                @* --- START: COMPANY PHOTO MODIFICATION --- *@
                <div class="company-photo-container mt-4">
                    <img src="/images/804.jpeg" alt="PLS Team and Facility" class="company-photo" />
                </div>
                @* --- END: COMPANY PHOTO MODIFICATION --- *@

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    /* Shared background styles */
    .page-background-shared {
        background: url('/images/back.jpeg') no-repeat center center / cover;
        min-height: 100vh;
        position: relative;
    }

    .overlay-shared {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px) saturate(120%);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px) saturate(120%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* Styles for the main content card */
    .glass-card-about {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        color: #fff;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: auto;
    }

    /* --- START: MODIFIED LOGO STYLE --- */
    .company-logo-banner {
        max-width: 350px; /* Control the width of the logo */
        height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
        background: #fff; /* White background for the logo */
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    /* --- END: MODIFIED LOGO STYLE --- */

    .about-header h1 {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .lead-text {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0.5rem auto 0;
    }

    .section-divider {
        border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
        margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .about-section {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-icon {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

        .section-icon svg {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }

    .section-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-content p {
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }

    .roles-list {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding-left: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

        .roles-list li {
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

            .roles-list li::before {
                content: '✓';
                position: absolute;
                left: 0;
                color: #28a745;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

    .team-members {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .special-thanks {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
    }

    /* --- START: NEW STYLE FOR THE COMPANY PHOTO --- */
    .company-photo-container {
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .company-photo {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
    }
    /* --- END: NEW STYLE FOR THE COMPANY PHOTO --- */
</style>
